{
  "stem": "25598.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was terrified, because wherever they were soldiers, there was death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he-- he didn't approach me right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He sort of gave me some time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then he looked at me, and he had good in his face, like it wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he-- I let him come closer, and he didn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He just came closer, and he pushed me away a little bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he took the ax and he started to chop the wood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then he looked into the hut and he saw what's-- what's happening there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "His name was Peter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, in Romanian, his name was Petre.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he started to come to the hut [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and bring medication, and bring food, from time to time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this might have well saved a few lives, which might not have made it without medication or without this, particularly the food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, one day, when some of the people in the hut started to-- were able to start to talk, he told us that he was married to a Jewish girl and he had a four-year-old son.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And after he had been taken to the army, they were shipped up-- shipped out to some camp and he-- he never found out where they were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- or if they're still alive, for that matter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after about two weeks, Petre disappeared and we never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we never knew if he was caught helping us and was shot or punished in some way, or if his unit simply moved on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it was nice that he was there for as long as he was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I must say, in retrospect, that he took a risk helping us.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
